  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "hilbert-curve",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/hilbert-curve/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.8,
      "size": 28800,
      "text": "一条一维的线，能不能填满整个二维的正方形？"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "hilbert-curve",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/hilbert-curve/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.02,
      "size": 32256,
      "text": "直觉上不可能，可数学家希尔伯特给出了肯定的答案。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "hilbert-curve",
      "section_id": "construct",
      "line_id": "con-2",
      "filename": "construct-con-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/hilbert-curve/construct-con-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.18,
      "size": 34848,
      "text": "升一阶时，把正方形切成四块，每块放一条小 U 形。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "hilbert-curve",
      "section_id": "construct",
      "line_id": "con-3",
      "filename": "construct-con-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/hilbert-curve/construct-con-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.29,
      "size": 36720,
      "text": "再把四条小曲线适当旋转翻转，首尾相接成一条大曲线。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "hilbert-curve",
      "section_id": "locality",
      "line_id": "loc-1",
      "filename": "locality-loc-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/hilbert-curve/locality-loc-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.66,
      "size": 26496,
      "text": "这条曲线最迷人的性质，是它的邻近保持。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "hilbert-curve",
      "section_id": "locality",
      "line_id": "loc-2",
      "filename": "locality-loc-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/hilbert-curve/locality-loc-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.16,
      "size": 34560,
      "text": "沿曲线走，位置相近的两点，在平面上几乎总是紧挨着。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "hilbert-curve",
      "section_id": "locality",
      "line_id": "loc-3",
      "filename": "locality-loc-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/hilbert-curve/locality-loc-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.09,
      "size": 33408,
      "text": "于是二维的邻近关系，被巧妙地压进了一维的顺序里。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "hilbert-curve",
      "section_id": "apply",
      "line_id": "app-1",
      "filename": "apply-app-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/hilbert-curve/apply-app-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.43,
      "size": 38880,
      "text": "图像处理里，用它扫描像素能让相邻像素在数据流中也相邻。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "hilbert-curve",
      "section_id": "apply",
      "line_id": "app-2",
      "filename": "apply-app-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/hilbert-curve/apply-app-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.33,
      "size": 37296,
      "text": "数据库和地理索引用它把二维坐标编码成一维键，加速范围查询。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "hilbert-curve",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/hilbert-curve/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.29,
      "size": 36720,
      "text": "调整阶数，看曲线如何一层层加密，把正方形填得越来越满。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "hilbert-curve",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/hilbert-curve/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.33,
      "size": 37296,
      "text": "打开折点，观察渐变色如何标出从起点到终点的遍历顺序。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "hilbert-curve",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/hilbert-curve/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.89,
      "size": 30240,
      "text": "希尔伯特曲线用递归拼接，连续填满整个平面。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "hilbert-curve",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/hilbert-curve/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.95,
      "size": 31248,
      "text": "它的邻近保持让一维顺序忠实地记住二维的远近。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "hilbert-curve",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-3",
      "filename": "summary-sum-3.mp3",
